Package Game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    Models the Goban used in a game of go.
    Constants
    Contains the constants present in the protocol.
    EnforceRule
    Class containing the static function that is responsible for removing the stones from the board.
    Group
    Models a group of intersections and their liberties.
    History
    Simple class containing the history of a Go Game.
    Intersection
    Models the intersection of a Goban.
    MoveValidator
    Checks if a move is a valid move regarding the go rules.
    Score
    The Score class contains the static functions that are able to calculate scores after a game of Go.
